Megatron Revived:
 
After hearing the news of bots being found in the mining region, Megatron deployed himself to maintain a security issue.  He made his way stealthily to the old base and landed sveral hundred meters away.  He fley in robot mode toward the base and waited for a moment where he was sure it was deserted and aimed a comm message at the base alone.
 
"Blacknightmare, this is Megatron.  Are you there?"
